metadata.name: Euterpe Genesis @ 2023
metadata.description:
You must hold Whitelist and SBT at the same time to participate in the 1st round of Euterpe IP-NFT Public Mint. SBT - Mint Your Creative Soul, which represents your artistic taste and creative energy, can be used as your PFP and a status symbol (soul) in the Euterpe ecosystem. (Non-transferable)  

Euterpe IP-NFT starts with Music IP. Currently, Euterpe has reached cooperation with a number of well-known Asian artists, including Zhou Shen, Shan Yichun, and PET CONSPIRACY. Euterpe IP-NFT holders can earn the royalties generated when the songs increase in popularity, which will revolutionize the income distribution system of the music industry. 

Be an Euterpe IP-NFT Holder now and earn royalties with your favorite artists!
